›—ظVarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-01-05-nushell_0_25.mdظ@7fed6d2cd79367f1d903dfbe54a850cca8e802f0495fab1eb1f7e409071aba38³title: Nushell 0.25‘¬Nushell 0.25ع½



Nushell, or Nu for short, is a new shell that takes a modern, structured approach to your commandline. It works seamlessly with the data from your filesystem, operating system, and a growing number of file formats to make it easy to build powerful commandline pipelines.
Today, we're releasing 0.25 of Nu. It's one of the largest releases we've ever done. With it Nushell grows from being a shell to being a full scripting language as well.
’گگعôTitle: title: Nushell 0.25
Path: Nushell 0.25
Content:




Nushell, or Nu for short, is a new shell that takes a modern, structured approach to your commandline. It works seamlessly with the data from your filesystem, operating system, and a growing number of file formats to make it easy to build powerful commandline pipelines.
Today, we're releasing 0.25 of Nu. It's one of the largest releases we've ever done. With it Nushell grows from being a shell to being a full scripting language as well.
—ظVarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-01-05-nushell_0_25.mdظ@4390839111f3c2dfd8399e2164824900d725c9fbacc507335edde219e0b527e9³title: Nushell 0.25‘¯Where to get itعكNu 0.25 is available as 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/releases/tag/0.25.1] pre-built binaries
 or from 
[link: https://crates.io/crates/nu] crates.io
. If you have Rust installed you can install it using 
``cargo install nu``
.
If you want all the goodies, you can install 
``cargo install nu --features=extra``
.
As part of this release, we also publish a set of plugins you can install and use with Nu. To install, use 
``cargo install nu_plugin_<plugin name>``
.
